oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Farrow Amusements (undated)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Carnivals; Fairs;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color half sheet (blue on white) announcing Farrow Amusements. This poster is probably a stock item, which Hatch would print during slow months. The shop would add events details once Farrow Amusements called and ordered posters.
